<h2>Our Step-by-Step LG Dryer Spinning Repair Process</h2>
<p>When you call (323) 990-7550, we dispatch our nearest technician to your location within 2-4 hours. Upon arrival, our tech conducts a comprehensive diagnostic sequence starting with visual inspection of the drum mechanism and belt system. We manually rotate the drum to check for binding, examine roller assemblies for wear patterns, and test motor engagement through the drive coupling.</p>
