  replace belt only and it fails again within months</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>Next comes electrical diagnosis using specialized meters to verify motor windings, capacitor function, and control board signals. For DLGX4001W and similar models, we access the rear panel to inspect the idler pulley assembly and drive belt routing. Our technicians carry OEM replacement belts, rollers, and motor components for immediate repairs.</p>
<p>The repair phase involves careful disassembly of the drum assembly when necessary, precise belt routing following LG specifications, and calibrated tension adjustment.</p>
